<p class="h1">BORROW, BORROWING</p>
<p class="fl">Receiving money or goods that one pledges to return. The Mosaic law regulated borrowing and lending (<a href="?bref=Deut.23.19-20">Dt 23:19-20</a>). <span class="ital">See</span> <a href="?item=BankerBanking_Article_TyndaleOpenBibleDictionary">Banker, Banking</a>.</p>
